<D>__{then four long years more alone in his never finished, already decaying, pleasure palace, aloof, seldom visited, never photographed, charles foster kane continued to direct his falling empire ... vainly attempting to sway, as he once did, the destinies of a nation that has ceased to listen to him ... ceased to trust him...}
